    "title": "Reliance Digital Global Group is Hiring: Floor Manager (Entry-Level)",
    "description": "Join the Reliance Digital Global Group family as a Floor Manager in Chennai. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout Reliance Digital Global Group:\nReliance Digital Global Group is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Maintain high standards of store hygiene and cleanliness\n• Handle customer queries, complaints, and escalations effectively\n• Achieve sales targets and improve store performance metrics\n• Manage store operations to ensure smooth daily functioning\n• Ensure visual merchandising standards are maintained at all times\n• Conduct regular stock audits and prevent pilferage\n• Build relationships with regular customers to drive loyalty\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Retail Operations\n• Proficiency in Loyalty Programs\n• Proficiency in Visual Merchandising\n• Proficiency in Sales Techniques\n• Proficiency in KPI Management\n• Proficiency in E-commerce Integration\n• Proficiency in SAP Retail\n• Proficiency in Customer Service\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Learning & development budget\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Chennai, Tamil Nadu, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Reliance Digital Global Group!",
